						<li><img src="model images/option/sonata hybrid/sola roof.jpg" class="optionImg"><br><p style="font-weight:bold;"><input type="checkbox" name="option_4" value="파노라마 선루프">파노라마 선루프</p> 1,200,000원</li>
					</ul>
